name: Tittsworth
description: '''Jesse Tittsworth''' (born February 26, 1979), better known under his stage name '''Tittsworth''', is an American DJ, producer, nightclub owner, and record label owner. He has worked on projects with [[Q-Tip (musician)|Q-Tip]], [[Theophilus London]], [[Pitbull (rapper)|Pitbull]], [[Kid Sister]] and [[Alvin Risk]]. He co-founded T&A Records, Hermanito Label, and [[U Street Music Hall]].
